structure 5vn3-1rz8-hybrid-open-sym_N2-extended-to-TM-from-685-declash-crot.psf
coordinates 5vn3-1rz8-hybrid-open-sym_N2-extended-to-TM-from-685-declash-crot.pdb
bincoordinates 5vn3-1rz8-hybrid-open-sym_N2-extended-to-TM-from-685-declash-crot.coor
